Create the file in VS Code named `.gitignore` and add this:
```
# Environment files - NEVER commit these
.env
.env.local
.env.production
.env.staging

# Secret files
*.key
*.pem
*.cert
secrets/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Mac files
.DS_Store

# Logs
*.log